{"tid":1116358,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港星錢小豪來台遇強震 居然說「我很開心！」","createTime":"2019-04-20T02:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T03:58:09.000Z","uid":164771,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"773723820aa51b289c931ba85ab93d5bea07cfb9","tid":1116358,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T02:09:59.000Z","msg":"1980年代憑一系列殭屍電影，紅遍港台的56歲港星錢小豪，今（18）日來台出席紅心字會30週年「豪心有豪報」公益環島活動記者會，並且帶著帥氣的大兒子龐景峰出席，力挺進入演藝圈40個年頭的爸爸做公益，沒想到記者會才剛始，居然就發生全台大地震。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只見到現場搖得很厲害，連家具和燈都不斷巨烈搖晃，這時錢小豪卻相當淡定，一點也不害怕，還直言：「我沒有嚇到，我反而很開心，因為我在香港沒有看過，不過還是希望大家平安。」至於站在旁邊的兒子表情也非常鎮定，只淡淡地說：「因為在外國求學經常遇到，所以不會怕。」態度不慌不忙。"},{"pid":"2a7806066904f20e35892d99b73538e71b4a294f","tid":1116358,"uid":132587,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"真係弱智<br />\n就算真係開心都唔好講出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a21291ce5c4547d85c11b23bf107c134b0c8af","tid":1116358,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"2a7806066904f20e35892d99b73538e71b4a294f","tid":1116358,"uid":132587,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"真係弱智<br />\n就算真係開心都唔好講出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T02:23:01.000Z","msg":"後面果句又當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c237d65cb42596b687c9a195fe17a2d1b7bc00ee","tid":1116358,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T02:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f706222724a2ce8299c77e41c451fcfb729520da","tid":1116358,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"地震有好多女露裙底<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180820/bkn-20180820132426213-0820_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link